ğŸ§  AI Code Review App (MERN Stack + Gemini API)
This is a full-stack web application built using the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) that allows users to write, review, and get AI-generated feedback on their code. It leverages Google's Gemini LLM API to provide intelligent and contextual code reviews, optimization suggestions, and improvement tips.

